{"tid":1203781,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"金鐘無理搜袋一事證明係現場唔一定要衝擊, 但一定要出現到現場","createTime":"2019-06-11T13:25:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T13:53:07.000Z","uid":67294,"like":33,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"852d1f04aca5915833a68365e343254abdaae659","tid":1203781,"uid":67294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T13:25:30.000Z","msg":"警察無理搜袋, 引起民憤<br />\n現場所有市民即刻抗議比群眾壓力<br />\n最後警方收隊<br />\n<br />\n試諗下如果當時金鐘站無人出聲, 你估結局會唔會係咁?<br />\n所以一定要出黎, 你既出席己經可以支持整個活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2a96c063eb7ef9e17dd20128310a2b7036b4b12","tid":1203781,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T13:44:23.000Z","msg":"岩呀"},{"pid":"5658a1e302b2648c251e8d96f28fd0a900acd5f5","tid":1203781,"uid":81113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T13:44:48.000Z","msg":"明日第一班車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eff7c80d94e23a3eb63ff3e9468991be6bd54d3","tid":1203781,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T13:44:55.000Z","msg":"被無理搜身要注意事項<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/cLtcdS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/cLtcdS</a>"},{"pid":"a450bf59a67b9dd9ad890cf7ecafd453f9d17482","tid":1203781,"uid":167938,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T13:44:58.000Z","msg":"Im coming bro<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f9201a90575576513a2d69931dd64d9c205fed4","tid":1203781,"uid":171192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T13:45:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港人加油！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"4c5a3df7a473aa91ef0e5a3be6edec9fc535a566","tid":1203781,"uid":157362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T13:48:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"92c43b3b3bd42580d10d1688bd12338403c219ca","tid":1203781,"uid":184746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T13:49:31.000Z","msg":"5.如何辨認警務人員之身份/警察委任證之真偽？<br />\n<br />\n警務人員在以下情況須出示警察委任證：<br />\n<br />\n便衣警務人員：在行使警察權力時，必須表明身分及出示委任證。<br />\n<br />\n軍裝警務人員：一般無須主動出示警察委任證，但如市民提出要求，他們亦須出示委任證，除非情況不容許，或要求不合理。<br />\n<br />\n　　<br />\n當警務人員出示委任證，只須向提出要求的市民展示委任證，而不可將委任證轉交任何市民查閱。&nbsp;<span style=\"color: teal;\"><strong><em>如市民對警務人員身份或委任證存有懷疑，可立即聯絡就近警署&nbsp;查詢</em></strong></span>。"},{"pid":"1d17099b0613f438495e96e8865148ecaf5ac35f","tid":1203781,"uid":178533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T13:53:07.000Z","msg":"推"}]}